## How to respond

Add **one** of these tags to this BKD issue (`{{ intent_issue_id }}`):

- `acceptance:approve` — sisyphus archives the PRs and finishes the REQ.
- `acceptance:request-changes` — sisyphus starts a `dev` fixer round.
  Write the specific feedback as a chat follow-up here; sisyphus picks up
  the most recent user message as the fixer's brief.
- `acceptance:reject` — sisyphus aborts the REQ. (Equivalent: close this
  BKD issue / set status to "done" without an `acceptance:approve` tag.)

You can also leave it sitting — there is no watchdog timeout on this
state. The REQ waits as long as you need.
